						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Other-commodities/Coffee/Relevant-publications/Value-Adding-Agro-Enterprise-and-Poverty-Reduction-A-territorial-approach-for-Rural-Business-Development" title="Value Adding, Agro Enterprise and Poverty Reduction: A territorial approach for Rural Business Development" alt="document">Value Adding, Agro Enterprise and Poverty Reduction: A territorial approach for Rural Business Development</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p> Paragraph 4.4 of this article gives an example of coffee farmers who have managed to make their coffee more profitable despite the bad market situation. <a href="http://webapp.ciat.cgiar.org/agroempresas/pdf/value_adding.pdf" target="_blank">Download PDF</a> </p>
