<h2><a class="listing" style="document" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Other-commodities/Coffee/Relevant-publications/Press-release-on-improved-quality-of-Arabica-coffee-genome" title="Press release on improved quality of Arabica coffee genome" alt="document">Press release on improved quality of Arabica coffee genome</a></h2>

	
	
	
	
					<p> Brazilian scientists finished mapping the arabica coffee genome with the aim of raising the tree's resistance to disease and harsh weather and improving quality (from the author’s introduction). <a href="http://ccr.ucdavis.edu/biot/new/arabica.html" target="_blank">Download document</a> </p>
